sequenceDiagram
    participant R as Registry (ghcr.io/opensource-distroless)
    participant S as Source (Adoptium OpenJDK)
    participant GH as GitHub Action (Java Assembler)
    participant Sec as Security (Cosign/Hash)
    
    GH->>R: Pull `cc:latest`
    R-->>GH: Download strictly verified Opensource Distroless foundation
    GH->>Sec: `cosign verify` cc:latest ancestry
    Sec-->>GH: Pass
    
    GH->>S: curl Temurin21-binaries.tar.gz
    S-->>GH: Java Application Payload
    GH->>Sec: Confirm sha256 checksums match Adoptium origins
    
    GH->>GH: `FROM cc:latest` \n Overlay JRE into `/usr/lib/jvm`
    
    GH->>R: Push Execution Container (java:latest)
    GH->>Sec: `cosign sign` Final OCI Manifest
